{"tid":1909632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter戰線：要求YouTube踢走營利門檻","createTime":"2020-03-04T05:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T15:24:53.000Z","uid":264529,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6eaf07c136578705a645fd77e75bfdab1bc39902","tid":1909632,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"https:/<a href=\"http://twitter.com/lottery248/status/1232211549856493569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flottery248%2Fstatus%2F1232211549856493569&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=3685ee2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flottery248%2Fstatus%2F1232211549856493569&h=f6dacf39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/lottery248/status/1232211549856493569</a><br />\n小弟親自用英文寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶人包：<br />\n講門檻其實會三輸，因為係變相打壓庶民，但啲人工同有名氣channel卻多數無事，咁玩法會令YT失去多元化嘅特性同更難搵到人才<br />\n<br />\n幾戇鳩都好，唔少同今次無關嘅channel都有類似嘅遭遇，幫手乘勢起革命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451cdb13d5961c6076e34a666e27ad90aeaa8bb9","tid":1909632,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"Retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1a395d56d0206239bc4e82b5fcf4c1387dc6ae","tid":1909632,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:02:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1f90bed8d07eecb7359d52acbbe89f1f810ee3b","tid":1909632,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"仲有 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lottery248/status/1232211549856493569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flottery248%2Fstatus%2F1232211549856493569&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=352bd206\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flottery248%2Fstatus%2F1232211549856493569&h=836e5b28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lottery248/status/1232211549856493569</a><br />\n(link係詳細版)"},{"pid":"194adcc857f7f9047fc1a8f213f9ae79cc8ca678","tid":1909632,"uid":115096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:03:54.000Z","msg":"其實個門檻應該由廣告客戶決定"},{"pid":"0b93574d3b02d7397c27837e9dc8f1471cad7dc5","tid":1909632,"uid":124247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"等我幫你rt先"},{"pid":"e7912084ae2f40dee0be4253f5188e18157d2276","tid":1909632,"uid":264529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194adcc857f7f9047fc1a8f213f9ae79cc8ca678","tid":1909632,"uid":115096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:03:54.000Z","msg":"其實個門檻應該由廣告客戶決定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"佢地嘅決定未必一樣<br />\n加上佢地可以自己揀埋邊啲分類（唔）擺<br />\n當佢地控制得到嘅時候，門檻仲有咩用？<br />\n<br />\n仲有，黃標唔係得我地先係，有啲知名人（曾經）都畀人攪過<br />\n<br />\n今次係希望乘勢起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454f9a41c62572593b7de905ccf09726d17a8c83","tid":1909632,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"7de22fd3b9df001fabb531d6bc3defa042bb6424","tid":1909632,"uid":12